interpretation: The "sheaf of rice" card represents abundance, growth, and harvest. It symbolizes the rewards that come from hard work and dedication. This card reminds us that we reap what we sow and that our efforts will be rewarded in due time. It can also signify a time of plenty, where we have more than enough of what we need. Alternatively, this card can represent a need for patience and perseverance, as the fruits of our labor may not be immediately visible. Associated keywords include prosperity, success, patience, diligence, and gratitude. Overall, the "sheaf of rice" card is a positive and uplifting symbol of abundance and growth, encouraging us to continue working towards our goals with dedication and optimism.
